column2: SELECT TOP #   a.OBJID AS OBJID,   a.RA AS RA,   a.DEC AS DEC,      /*   sp.z AS zsp,   sp.zErr AS e_zsp,   sp.class AS class,   sp.subClass AS subClass,   sp.zWarning AS zWarning,   sp.mode AS mode,   */   ph.ra AS RA_ph,   ph.dec AS DEC_ph,   ph.mode AS mode,   ph.probPSF AS probPSF, /* propability that object is the star */   ph.modelMag_u AS umag,   ph.modelMag_g AS gmag,   ph.modelMag_r AS rmag,   ph.modelMag_i AS imag,   ph.modelMag_z AS zmag,   ph.modelMagErr_u AS e_umag,   ph.modelMagErr_g AS e_gmag,   ph.modelMagErr_r AS e_rmag,   ph.modelMagErr_i AS e_imag,   ph.modelMagErr_z AS e_zmag        from   MyDB.akari AS a   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( a.RA, a.RA, #) AS n   JOIN PhotoObjAll as ph ON n.objid = sp.objid    /* JOIN */ where   a.OBJID < #
